## Modules

### Patient
- Register Account
- Login
- Book Appointment
- View Appointment Details

### Doctor
- Login
- View Patient Appointments
- Manage Appointments

### Admin
- Login
- Manage Doctors
- Manage Patients
- Generate Appointment Reports

## Installation

1. Clone the repository.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/NETRA-Eye-Care-Hospital.git
```

2. Copy the project into the **htdocs** folder (XAMPP) or **www** folder (WAMP).

3. Import the MySQL database into **phpMyAdmin**.

4. Start **Apache** and **MySQL**.

5. Open your browser and visit:

```
http://localhost/NETRA-Eye-Care/
```

## Requirements

- PHP 7.4 or above
- MySQL
- Apache Server (XAMPP/WAMP/LAMP)
- Web Browser

